Tracy.John C. Kimball High School: John C. Kimball High School (KHS) is an American public comprehensive high school in Tracy, California, south of 11th Street on Lammers Road. Kimball High School is the third comprehensive high school in the Tracy Unified School District and also serves the planned area of Mountain House. The first day of school was August 12, 2009 with an enrollment of 1,472 students.
